text: Singapore Blue color Downtown line MRTstation no34 this station open at 21oct 2017.. this Located under upper changi Road east this station served Residential estates in the Vicinity and campus of the Singapore University of Technology and Design,which linked via Underground link way.. ......
Still relatively new with only a bubble tea shop and no direct access to SUTD. Toilets are clean and well-maintained.
Singapore Blue DownTown line Stan no_34,  Near Changi airport ,next Station Expo 35no

Im using the tourist pass card and it is my last day here. So i asked the Indian officer at the counter where can i return the pass to claim back my deposit. He mentioned that it can be done at Terminal 4 (of where im heading to) confidently. As i arrived at Terminal 4, I was instructed to go to Terminal 2 instead for the claim.

So thank you dear officer for the false info and making me go around changi. You should  get a raise for being so “clever”
Very weird station design-wise.  Most of the exits lack escalators, only an elevator. B2 is completely inaccessible. Overbuilt station for sure. There's direct access to SUTD though.
